page.title: 16LIFE STYLES
page.content: Everyday I get up with my dog Max at 7:30 am ,then we get washed and dressed. Afterwards myself and my family have breakfast. At 8:15am. I say "Goodbye," to my dad and set off for school. School starts at 8:50am.when we have registration.At 9:00am.we have assembly on three mornings a week. Lessons go on until break at 10:30am. and continue at 12:00pm. Lunch time lasts one and a quater hours, in which time I either play in the playground or use the computers in the computer area. Afternoon lessons continue from 1:15 pm until hometime at 3:20pm. Dad picks me up after school.Then somtimes my friends come round.At six I have tea then I watch T.V. Then I go to bed at 9:30pm.
